# Styling Rules

- **Tailwind CSS only** — no custom CSS except `globals.css` for CSS variable definitions.
- Tenant theme via CSS variables: `var(--color-primary)`, `var(--color-secondary)`, `var(--color-accent)`.
- Use `cn()` utility (clsx + tailwind-merge) for all conditional class merging.
- Dark mode: class-based `dark:` prefix, toggled via `useUIStore`.
- RTL: use Tailwind logical properties: `ps-`, `pe-`, `ms-`, `me-`, `start-`, `end-`.
- Font sizes: Tailwind scale only (`text-sm`, `text-base`, `text-lg`) — no arbitrary values.
- Spacing: Tailwind scale only (`p-4`, `gap-6`) — no arbitrary values.
- Border radius: use CSS variable `--radius` from shadcn/ui config.
- No hardcoded color hex values in className — always use CSS variable or Tailwind semantic class.
- Animations: use `motion/react` (`motion.div`, `AnimatePresence`) — no CSS keyframes except loading spinners.
